org.ObjectLayout.examples

Class Octagon

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ObjectLayout.examples.Octagon

  • public class Octagon
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple org.ObjectLayout.examples.Octagon class example with an intrinsic StructuredArray of Points. Demonstrates use of IntrinsicObjectModel members and their initialization, when the intrinsic member is a StructuredArray.
